{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_07_01",
  "title": "白石沙季 1話 目指せスリクス",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です\n少々お時間をいただいてもいいでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ good work.\nMay I have a moment of your time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.6666666627,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。どうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work. What's up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.7986164529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "先ほど、さとみさんからアイドルが出場する\nダンス大会の話を聞いたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just now‚ Satomi-san told me about\nidols participating in a dance competition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4333334882,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、そのことか。ちょうどみんなに知らせようと\n思ってたんだ。この番組なんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ about that. I was just about to let everyone know.\nIt's this program…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.0860994298,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2247.2339034999995,
          "startTime": 20.3333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "あ……この番組、知ってます\n人気アイドルが沢山出演する配信番組ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… I know this program.\nIt's a streaming show where many popular idols come out‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0333330432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "生配信をすれば同時接続二万人超えが当たり前で\nアーカイブの再生回数も平均で数十万回……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it's a live stream‚ exceeding 20‚000 viewers is normal thing‚\nand the average number of archive views is in the hundreds of thousands…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.6333330432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "私もよく、千紗や雫ちゃんと観ています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I often watch it with Chisa and Shizuku-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.5573891917,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "知ってるなら話が早いな。今回はこの番組で\n特別にダンス大会が開かれることになってな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you know about it‚ then it's straightforward. This time‚\nthere will be a special dance competition on this show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.0056915561,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "とはいっても、普通のダンス大会じゃない。自分が\n所属するグループ以外の曲で踊らなきゃいけないんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it's not just any dance competition. Participants have to\ndance to songs from groups other than their own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.0390259067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……決められた期間内に、他人の曲でどれだけ\nダンスを仕上げられるかを競うんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… So it's a competition to see how well you can prepare\ndances to other people's songs within a set period.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.3000004728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルのいつもと違うパフォーマンスが見られる\nという視聴者サービスも兼ねているらしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's also a service for viewers to see\nidols performing differently from usual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.3422913988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ちょうど、大会への参加の打診がきたところで\nこれからみんなに希望をとろうとしてたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just as we received an offer to participate in the competition‚\nI was about to ask everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.5089570482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "その大会……私に出場させてもらえないでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About that competition… Could I participate?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.3756237149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "沙季が？　熱意は嬉しいが……\nスケジュール的にかなり厳しいと思うぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You‚ Saki? I appreciate your enthusiasm‚ but…\nI think it'll be quite challenging schedule-wise‚ don't you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.2402496457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "心配していただいてありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for your concern.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.6402496457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "最近、レギュラーでいただけるお仕事があって\nありがたいなと思っていたんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Recently‚ I've been getting regular work‚\nwhich I'm grateful for.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.2666661222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "それと同時に、もっと新しいことにも\nチャレンジして成長出来ないかと思っていたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At the same time‚ I've been thinking about\nchallenging myself and growing in new ways.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.099999996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "今回は個人参加ですから、スケジュールの隙間時間を\nやりくりすれば、無理なく準備出来そうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since this is an individual participation‚ if I manage my schedule gaps‚\nI think I can prepare for it without any problem.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.8666727344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。正式に決まり次第連絡するよ\n誰の曲で踊りたいか、希望はあるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Got it. I'll let you know as soon as it's settled.\nDo you have any preferences for whose song you'd like to dance to?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.9826595266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "……スリクスの曲で踊らせてもらえないでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Could I dance to IIIX's song?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.5493114431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスの曲を……？　理由を聞かせてくれるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "IIIX's song…? Can you tell me the why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.2215559284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITYで負けた相手ですし……なぜあんなにも\n強いのか、改めて研究したかったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They were the opponents we lost to in I-UNITY…\nI wanted to study why they're so strong again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.333323125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "それに、期限を決めずに漫然と分析するよりも\n今回のような機会を活かした方がいいのでは……と",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ rather than aimlessly analyzing without a deadline‚\nI thought it would be better to make use of an opportunity like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.033323125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "締め切りがある上に、彼女達の曲で踊るのを沢山の人の\n前で披露する。これは絶好のチャンスだと思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With a deadline‚ performing in front of many people\nwith their song‚ I think this is a great chance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.6666564583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そこまで考えてるなら……分かった\nスリクスに楽曲を使う件を伝えておくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you're thinking that far ahead… I see.\nI'll inform IIIX about using their music.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.4797419032,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you so much!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.5797337652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "本人達に見てもらえたら一番いいだろうけど……\n彼女達のスタンスを考えると、難しいだろうな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It would be best if they could see it themselves…\nBut considering their stance‚ it might be difficult.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.7111017108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_01-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "確かにそうですね。でも、お気になさらないで下さい\n出来る限り自分で分析してみます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true. But please don't worry.\nI'll try to analyze as much as I can on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.3666411994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.8108834307,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.8442310055
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.8442310055
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
